{"tid":1252094,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"祝緒丹疑有靚仔男友","createTime":"2019-06-22T21:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T13:10:12.000Z","uid":85180,"like":21,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"da7e9941253fb64e9d97db9849b731181e2ae092","tid":1252094,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T21:05:27.000Z","msg":"祝緒丹疑有靚仔男友<br />\n<br />\n據內地媒體指出，就在近日她被影到身穿一襲黑色外衣，並戴上漁夫帽顯得十分低調地出現在北京某餐廳。當中除了她之外身邊還出現一男一女，同時地他們二人亦是戴上帽。就在他們三人用完餐之後，男方就開車準備離開，此時祝緒丹並無同同行女子選擇坐後座，而是直奔坐副駕座有如女主人似的。就在他們落車之後就齊齊走去玩密室逃脫遊戲，途中祝緒丹的鞋帶鬆脫，該男子就第一時間跪下幫她綁好，之後大家並列向前走男方還主動手摸她的臀部，而她第一時間作出反射條件推開，之後此男子再次手摸她就無避開，還傾得好開心添！或者有一些人會覺得可能是好朋友而已，但其實好朋友之間都要分明「男女授受不親」的道理，相信大部份女士都不會無緣無故被男友人摸臀吧？所以由此證明他們疑是男女朋友，而另一女友人極可能只是用作掩飾而已。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OqMwWpq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOqMwWpq.jpg&h=97b56c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4adbWpr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4adbWpr.jpg&h=5253cc2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAi3Nv7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAi3Nv7.jpg&h=83b314dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yuOOYCR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyuOOYCR.jpg&h=04069419&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n摸屁股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n綁鞋帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7bb44db5eadcc4a7cf14023b0709222cf1ccce","tid":1252094,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T21:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc94e54ce164a271341ba55227d8d36e81c87d8","tid":1252094,"uid":89595,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T21:17:13.000Z","msg":"邊撚個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9858